    <p>This is a small space that seats 24, with an open kitchen tak­ing up al­most half the shop­house space.</p>
    <p>Ta­bles for two can be joined up for groups of four, with j ust enough space in be­tween to sat­isfy safe-dis­tanc­ing reg­u­la­tions.</p>
    <p>Light earth tones give the room a warm feel­ing, though a large lit sign of the restau­rant’s name at the back adds a play­ful touch.</p>
    <p>An ex­cel­lent show­case of how hawker dishes can in­spire fine cui­sine with­out be­ing gim­micky or over­priced.</p>

